content: Hi! My name's Jim. I'm from New Zealand. This is my friend. His name's Adam. He's from Australia. This is my friend too. Her name's Paola. She's from Italy. This is another friend. He's from Greece. This is my friend Hayley. She's from Australia too. This is my friend Gabriela. She's from Argentina. What's your name? Where are you from?
